snippet.title: Longplay of Need for Speed: Underground Rivals (1/2)
snippet.description:
Longplay of Need for Speed: Underground Rivals, played as the NTSC version on the PlayStation Portable. This game's version was released on Mar. 14th, 2005. Please give the video a like! Timecodes are below:

Part (2/2): https://youtu.be/h0PzO_6p8vU

3:20:29 - Novice: Rally Relay 1-12
4:14:35 - Drag 3-6

7:56:07 - Car Spec: WRX STi Spec 1-3
8:15:04 - Pro: Rally Relay 1-12

By: Val
